4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with essential programming skills in JavaScript and Python. The program spans 18 weeks, incorporating 16 weeks of classes followed by 2 weeks for project development, with a class size ratio of 1 instructor to 7 students. No prior coding skills are needed, and classes are available in both English and Spanish.

Students will learn web development, algorithm scripting, and how to utilize APIs for enhanced functionality. The curriculum culminates in a hands-on project presentation. Instructors include experienced professionals from VMware, ensuring mentorship from industry experts.

